The dried, hard, crusty elbow is now almost in two peices (torn by the
clamp). May have been like that before or could have been my forgetfulness,
probably both.

Does anyone know where to get a new rubber alt. elbow? This is the elbow
between the alt. and the fan housing. Bus-boys say NLA with part#
021-903-655B. However, I googled 022-903-655 and found one (Automobile
Atlanta) for a 914 but $30! and a few pages in German. Or can I glue this
one back together?
